physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Dysmorphological examination revealed coarse face, high forehead, bitemporal narrowing, deep-set eyes, prominent nasal bridge, bulbous nasal tip, short philtrum, thin lips, prominent jaw, posteriorly rotated ears, short neck, obesity, tapering fingers, brachydactyly, bilateral sandal gaps between the first and second toes, acanthosis nigricans on the neck, and striae on the abdominal region. No abnormalities were noted in other systemic evaluations.
